dc_description_s: This point data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Outagamie_PLSS_2018.gdb. [Outagamie County related Public Land Survey System information. This is a feature class representing the section corners within Outagamie County. These points were established previously and eventually all were reset by Outagamie County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
